 to-do application with synchronization capabilities.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-03-06T03:05:11.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tools and Apps</h2><h3>Habit Trackers</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://wakatime.com/\">Waka Time</a> –  Open source plugin for knowing exactly how long you spend coding.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-03-05T23:40:03.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tools and Apps</h2><h3>Task Management</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/features/project-management/\">GitHub Projects</a> – A lesser known feature of GitHub, makes it easy to tie your project management process to your code.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-10-31T21:50:27.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tools and Apps</h2><h3>File Management</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://nextcloud.com\">Nextcloud</a> – The self-hosted productivity platform that keeps you in control.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-10-05T10:24:38.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tools and Apps</h2><h3>Note Management</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://simplenote.com/\">Simplenote</a> – Light, clean, and free. Simplenote is now available for iOS, Android, Mac, Windows, Linux, and the web.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-01-17T18:40:19.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tools and Apps</h2><h3>Note Management</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://workflowy.com/\">WorkFlowy</a> – Web-based outlining application for nested bulletin lists.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-01-17T18:40:19.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tools and Apps</h2><h3>Task Management</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/amitmerchant1990/pomolectron\">Pomolectron</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/amitmerchant1990/pomolectron\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">