tomation: freelance project tracking, timesheets, invoicing &#x26; real-time productivity feedback.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-01-17T18:40:19.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tools and Apps</h2><h3>Task Management</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.amazingmarvin.com/\">Amazing Marvin</a> – Marvin incorporates principles from behavioral psychology to help beat procrastination, feel in control and finish todo list.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-01-17T18:38:36.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tools and Apps</h2><h3>Task Management</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://airtable.com/\">Airtable</a> – Mix of spreadsheet and database to help organize work.</li>","updatedAt":"2018-10-09T01:20:28.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Websites</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://zenhabits.net/\">Zen Habits</a> – Blog by Leo Babauta with topics such as simplifying life.</li>","updatedAt":"2018-03-07T23:12:56.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tools and Apps</h2><h3>Task Management</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://kanbanflow.com\">KanbanFlow</a> – Kanban method task board with Pomodoro technique.</li>","updatedAt":"2018-03-07T23:09:08.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Websites</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.reddit.com/r/productivity/\">r/Productivity</a> – Productivity subreddit.</li>","updatedAt":"2018-03-07T23:06:59.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Websites</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://lifehacker.com/12-tips-and-tricks-to-work-faster-in-microsoft-outlook-1540483009\">12+ Tips and Tricks to Work Faster in Microsoft Outlook</a> – Tame your Outlook with these tips in order to get a little bit closer to the awesome <em>Inbox Zero</em>.</li>","updatedAt":"2018-02-22T17:58:06.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Websites</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://blog.rememberthemilk.com/post/116665489183/guest-post-advanced-gtd-with-remember-the-milk\">Advanced GTD with Remember The Milk</a> – A tutorial on how to implement GTD with <a href=\"https://www.rememberthemilk.com\">Remember the Milk</a>.</li>","updatedAt":"2018-02-22T17:58:06.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Websites</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://bulletjournal.com/\">The Bullet Journal</a> – A pen and paper method that turns a simple notebook into a highly efficient productivity tool.</li>","updatedAt":"2018-02-22T17:58:06.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tools and Apps</h2><h3>Task Automation</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/ahkscript/awesome-AutoHotkey\">Awesome AutoHotKey</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/ahkscript/awesome-AutoHotkey\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">1.7k</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":1677,\"repo\":\"ahkscript/awesome-AutoHotkey\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> – AutoHotKey is a free, open-source macro-creation and automation software for Windows that allows users to automate repetitive tasks.</li>","updatedAt":"2018-02-22T17:58:06.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tools and Apps</h2><h3>Task Management</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.vivifyscrum.com\">VivifyScrum</a> – Agile project management app for teams that deliver. Customizable Scrum and Kanban boards.</li>","updatedAt":"2018-02-22T11:12:35.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tools and Apps</h2><h3>Note Management</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://standardnotes.org/\">Standard Notes</a> – A simple and private notes app.</li>","updatedAt":"2018-01-02T22:26:42.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tools and Apps</h2><h3>Note Management</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.inkdrop.info/\">Inkdrop</a> – A cross-platform note taking app for Markdown lovers.</li>","updatedAt":"2017-12-27T14:06:39.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tools and Apps</h2><h3>Task Management</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.any.do/\">Any.do</a> – Simple interface, packed with features, currently the favorite to-do list manager at <a href=\"http://lifehacker.com/5924093/five-best-to-do-list-managers\">Lifehacker</a>.</li>","updatedAt":"2017-12-16T21:07:54.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tools and Apps</h2><h3>Task Management</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://hitask.com\">Hitask</a> – Easy Project and Task Management for Teams.</li>","updatedAt":"2017-12-16T21:07:54.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tools and Apps</h2><h3>Task Management</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.omnigroup.com/omnifocus\">OmniFocus</a> – A Getting Things Done based task manager for Mac OS X and iOS.</li>","updatedAt":"2017-12-16T21:07:54.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tools and Apps</h2><h3>Task Management</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.rememberthemilk.com\">Remember the Milk</a> – Great at managing tags for to-dos and location based tasks.</li>","updatedAt":"2017-12-16T21:07:54.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tools and Apps</h2><h3>Task Management</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://taskade.com\">Taskade</a> – Simple and collaborative task lists for teams.</li>","updatedAt":"2017-12-16T21:07:54.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tools and Apps</h2><h3>Task Management</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://taskwarrior.org/\">Taskwarrior</a> – An open source command line task manager. Flexible, fast, efficient, and unobtrusive.</li>","updatedAt":"2017-12-16T21:07:54.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tools and Apps</h2><h3>Task Management</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://timingapp.com/\">Timing</a> – Automatic time and productivity tracking for Mac. Helps you stay on track with your work and ensures no billable hours get lost if you are billing hourly.</li>","updatedAt":"2017-12-16T21:07:54.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tools and Apps</h2><h3>Task Management</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://todotxt.com/\">Todo.txt</a> – Tired of having complicated apps to organize your tasks? Todo.txt is a technique that uses a single <code>.txt</code> file to help you get the job done.</li>","updatedAt":"2017-12-16T21:07:54.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tools and Apps</h2><h3>Task Management</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://todoist.com/\">Todoist</a> – Powerful and cross-platform productivity tool.</li>","updatedAt":"2017-12-16T21:07:54.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tools and Apps</h2><h3>Task Management</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://trello.com\">Trello</a> – Kanban method task board.</li>","updatedAt":"2017-12-16T21:07:54.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Websites</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.43folders.com/izero\">Inbox Zero</a> – Rigorous approach to email management aimed at keeping the inbox (almost) empty at all times.</li>","updatedAt":"2017-11-10T01:49:17.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tools and Apps</h2><h3>Task Automation</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://ifttt.com\">IFTTT</a> – Allows you to create chains of conditional statements (called <em>recipes</em>) between web services in order to make the web work for you and boost your productivity.</li>","updatedAt":"2017-11-10T01:49:17.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tools and Apps</h2><h3>Task Automation</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://tasker.dinglisch.net/\">Tasker</a> – Android application that can perform context sensitive custom tasks (<em>e.g.</em> automatically turn on wifi when you arrive home).</li>","updatedAt":"2017-11-10T01:49:17.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tools and Apps</h2><h3>Task Automation</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://zapier.com/\">Zapier</a> – Automation tool that allows you to connect hundreds of web services and create automations between the processes.</li>","updatedAt":"2017-11-10T01:49:17.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tools and Apps</h2><h3>Note Management</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/hsbalar/preserver\">Preserver</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/hsbalar/preserver\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">206</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":206,\"repo\":\"hsbalar/preserver\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> – Notes organizer desktop app based on Electron.</li>","updatedAt":"2017-10-27T11:07:33.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tools and Apps</h2><h3>Habit Trackers</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://habitica.com\">Habitica</a> – Complete your real life daily goals in a role play game (previously called <em>HabitRPG</em>).</li>","updatedAt":"2017-04-04T12:31:02.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tools and Apps</h2><h3>File Management</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://mega.nz/\">Mega</a> – A very generous (50G from the get go) and highly secure cloud storage solution.</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-17T20:33:53.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tools and Apps</h2><h3>Note Management</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://evernote.com/\">Evernote</a> – Evernote can basically become your second brain and remember everything for you.</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-14T19:21:23.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tools and Apps</h2><h3>Note Management</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.google.com/keep/\">Google Keep</a> – A nice and simple Note management system tightly integrated with Google products.</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-14T19:21:23.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tools and Apps</h2><h3>Note Management</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.onenote.com/\">OneNote</a> – Very good Note management solution, but best for Windows users.</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-14T19:21:23.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tools and Apps</h2><h3>File Management</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.box.com\">Box</a> – Very good cloud storage solution for business customers.</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-13T18:17:05.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tools and Apps</h2><h3>File Management</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.dropbox.com\">Dropbox</a> – Simple, elegant and versatile (PC, Macs, Android...) cloud storage solution.</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-13T18:17:05.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tools and Apps</h2><h3>File Management</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.google.ca/drive/\">Google Drive</a> – Cloud storage solution deeply integrated in the Google ecosystem.</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-13T18:17:05.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tools and Apps</h2><h3>File Management</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://onedrive.live.com\">OneDrive</a> – Best cloud storage solution for Windows users.</li>","updatedAt":"2015-08-13T18:17:05.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Websites</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://lifehacker.com/5901487/rid-your-desktop-of-clutter-with-this-simple-trio-of-icons\">Rid Your Desktop of Clutter with This Simple Trio of Icons</a> – A little trick that has been keeping my desktop clean for years now.</li>","updatedAt":"2015-07-16T14:28:37.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Books</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://books.simonandschuster.ca/The-5-Choices/Kory-Kogon/9781476711713\">The 5 Choices</a> by Kory Kogon, Adam Merrill, Leena Rinne – An all around productivity methodology dealing with prioritization, scheduling, technology and energy management.</li>","updatedAt":"2015-07-15T21:07:43.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Books</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://gettingthingsdone.com/store/product.php?productid=17035&#x26;cat=3&#x26;page\">Getting Things Done</a> by David Allen – A very simple and efficient time-management method.</li>","updatedAt":"2015-07-11T15:56:02.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Websites</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://lifehacker.com/\">Lifehacker</a> – The go-to blog for tips, tricks, and downloads for getting things done.</li>","updatedAt":"2015-07-09T12:51:13.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Websites</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://pomodorotechnique.com/\">Pomodoro Technique</a> – Slice your tasks in 25 minute packages and get more done in less time.</li>","updatedAt":"2015-07-09T12:51:13.000Z"}]},"previous":{"id":"awesomes/github.com/lukasz-madon/awesome-remote-job","repo":"lukasz-madon/awesome-remote-job"},"next":{"id":"awesomes/github.com/tramcar/awesome-job-boards","repo":"tramcar/awesome-job-boards"}},"pageContext":{"type":"week","repo":"jyguyomarch/awesome-productivity","id":"awesomes/github.com/jyguyomarch/awesome-productivity","previousId":"awesomes/github.com/lukasz-madon/awesome-remote-job","nextId":"awesomes/github.com/tramcar/awesome-job-boards"}},"staticQueryHashes":["147714651","228695001","2744905544"]}